{"tid":808052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人類總是] 富婆疑網戀海外工程師 4年遭騙1.8億港元","createTime":"2018-09-06T04:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T06:32:34.000Z","uid":80516,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2b7a2a978a2b8809872302cffc3775dacb51cb","tid":808052,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"本港發生歷年來最巨額網戀騙案。警方在今年8月上旬接獲一名本地女子報案，指她在一個網上約會平台結識一名男子，對方自稱為身處海外的工程師，於14年5月至今年7月期間多次向受害人表示自己生意周轉困難，並向受害人索取金錢。受害人按指示多次匯款後懷疑受騙報案。案中損失金額約1.8億港元。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，女事主為一名商人，<span style=\"color: red;\">年約60歲</span>，騙徒自稱在英國任職工程師，聲稱遭人凍結資產向女事主求助，而男女雙方結交逾4年從未見面。<br />\n<br />\n案件列作「以欺騙手段取得財產」，交由灣仔警區重案組跟進，暫未有人被捕。警方呼籲市民在網上結交朋友時必須謹慎，不應隨便在互聯網上披露個人資料及照片。如有網上結識的陌生人以任何原因要求索取金錢，不要輕易相信，必需核實其身份。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180906/bkn-20180906122241094-0906_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180906%2Fbkn-20180906122241094-0906_00822_001.html&d=MCX7vY550BJdq83wKU8DrjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=99f06670\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180906/bkn-20180906122241094-0906_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n做左60年人都係白做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faffbe37983b0dee313d40a7574922d8ff62c256","tid":808052,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:16:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢D幾個電話email就跌過百萬既，唔係支那種我切囉！！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8937e0900467361260019ee3d4da856da87fd81","tid":808052,"uid":62321,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:29:33.000Z","msg":"而男女雙方結交逾4年從未見面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea8cafb153c073e4e788f8e48cae26c4feae19e","tid":808052,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而男女雙方結交逾4年從未見面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老實丫，警犬就算查到有乜離岸洗白錢都只會當冇事，前居可鑑！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea5b74d6d6ffe0c465794bd4774ad54a4f4d721","tid":808052,"uid":5289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:41:18.000Z","msg":"逃稅姐<br />\n<br />\n公開秘密黎"},{"pid":"cb26625476fac5e5e9d4643b8b08e32c7ce4f54f","tid":808052,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而男女雙方結交逾4年從未見面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢點最可疑，咁都會[跌]過億？？？加上條女做地產既，大家心撚照啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實丫，警犬就算查到有乜離岸洗白錢都只會當冇事，前居可鑑！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}